  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      At Bispebjerg Hospital we have introduced an Early Warning Score based triage system , called
      Bispebjerg Early Warning Score (BEWS), in order to identify critically ill patient on arrival
      at the emergency department. The purpose of this study is to validate our triage system.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
